text: Leslie O'Brien (8 April 1905 - 26 December 1967) was an Australian cricketer. He played eight first-class matches for New South Wales between 1937/38 and 1938/39. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1905 births Category:1967 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney
